e third non-French-language Canadian film submitted in that category after Attila Bertalan's 1990 invented-language film A Bullet to the Head and Zacharias Kunuk's 2001 Inuktitut-language feature Atanarjuat: The Fast Runner.\n\nShe co-founded Hamilton-Mehta Productions, with her husband, producer David Hamilton in 1996. She was awarded a Genie Award in 2003 for the screenplay of Bollywood/Hollywood. In May 2012, Mehta received the Governor General's Performing Arts Award for Lifetime Artistic Achievement, Canada's highest honour in the performing arts. Source: Wikidata; 01/08/2023", "biography_author": null, "date_of_biography": "2025-03-14T18:17:48.718112+11:00", "external_links": [{"id": 3865, "uri": "https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Deepa_Mehta"}], "uuid": "1bbfb9db-c7b0-4cdb-8e43-1adcf5c288f9", "source": {"name": "Vernon", "slug": "vernon"}, "source_identifier": "4594", "external_references": [{"id": 26770, "source": {"name": "Wikidata", "slug": "wikidata"}, "source_identifier": "Q299140"}, {"id": 28119, "source": {"name": "VIAF", "slug": "viaf"}, "source_identifier": "55317328"}, {"id": 28120, "source": {"name": "LOC Auth", "slug": "loc-auth"}, "source_identifier": "n96065172"}, {"id": 28121, "source": {"name": "WorldCat", "slug": "worldcat"}, "source_identifier": "lccn-n96065172"}], "date_modified": "2025-03-14T18:17:48.718386+11:00"}, {"id": 20088, "name": "Irby Smith", "roles_in_work": [{"id": 1987971, "title": "Major league (Captioned)", "work_id": 84222, "role": "co-producer", "role_id": 915, "is_primary": true}, {"id": 2277229, "title": "Young guns II (Captioned)", "work_id": 84227, "role": "co-producer", "role_id": 915, "is_primary": true}, {"id": 2138948, "title": "City slickers (Captioned)", "work_id": 84221, "role": "producer", "role_id": 1089, "is_primary": true}, {"id": 2647654, "title": "The Power of listening", "work_id": 76927, "role": "producer/director", "role_id": 31, "is_primary": true}, {"id": 863203, "title": "Performance appraisal: the human 